         MACRO ,
&LABEL   #RLLI &REG,&LITERAL
.*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
.*                                                                    *
.*       This macro enables you to get the address of a 'literal'     *
.*       in a baseless routine. The literal can be anything that is   *
.*       the operand of a DC instruction                              *
.*                                                                    *
.*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
&LABEL   LARL  &REG,=&LITERAL    address the literal
         MEND  ,
